Peter: Can you please pass me the salad cream?
Tony: excuse me?
Peter: Oh, I said-
Tony: No, I know what you said, I’m just...
body:
Peter: Can you please pass me the salad cream?

Tony: excuse me?

Peter: Oh, I said-

Tony: No, I know what you said, I’m just giving you a chance to correct yourself

Peter: But salad cream is amazing!

Tony, dead serious: If you don’t use ketchup, you’re not a part of this family
